description: General project description.
globs: *
---
- This is a command line tool to annotate plasmid sequences.
- It should have the following features:
	- it should be fast
	- it shoud be modular
	- it should be able to handle multiple file formats
	- it should be easy to use and feel good to use
	- it should accurately and deeply annotate the plasmid sequences
- the main files of the project are found within ./plannotate/*
    - subject to change, but at the time of writing:
		- annotate.py
		- bokeh_plot.py
		- infernal.py
		- logging_config.py
		- plannotate.py
		- resources.py
